headline: Becton Dickinson (BDX) Tops Q1 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Becton Dickinson (BDX) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 15.10% and 1.32%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
